parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "HPX",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "gcc/11.2.0",
      "boost/1.78.0-release",
      "cmake/3.22.0",
      "hwloc/2.6.0",
      "pmix/4.1.0",
      "openmpi/4.1.2"
    ],
    "resources": {
      "nodes": 8,
      "tasks_per_node": 2,
      "total_tasks": 16,
      "cpus_per_task": 24,
      "partition": "buran",
      "nodes_list": "buran[08-15]",
      "time_limit": "00:10:00",
      "job_name": "hpx-plainmpi-join-8node-%j",
      "output_file": "hpx-plainmpi-join-8node-%j.txt",
      "error_file": "error-%j.txt"
    },
    "execution": {
      "command": "mpi_executor",
      "arguments": [
        "-type",
        "stencil_1d",
        "-width",
        "384",
        "-steps",
        "1000",
        "-kernel",
        "compute_bound",
        "--hpx:threads=48"
      ],
      "iterations": [
        2**6,
        2**9,
        2**12,
        2**15,
        2**18,
        2**21,
        2**24
      ],
      "description": "distributed HPX (plain MPI + fork join executor) task bench 8 buran nodes, width 384 fixed width, from 2(6) to 2(24)"
    }
  }
}
```
